pandoc 

  to: pptx
  output-file: preview-colour-pptx.pptx
  embed-resources: true
  default-image-extension: png
  

metadata

  title: Preview Colour Example
  subtitle: Quarto Extension
  author:
    - name: Mickaël CANOUIL, _Ph.D._
      orcid: 0000-0002-3396-4549
      url: https://mickael.canouil.fr
  extensions:
    preview-colour:
      code: true
      text: true
      json: example-colours.json
      glyph:
        default: ●
        html: '&#9673;'
        latex: \\textbullet
        typst: ◉
        docx: ●
        pptx: ●
  

(W) [preview-colour] Alpha channel is not preserved in pptx; rendering the opaque colour for "rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)".

(W) [preview-colour] Keyword colour "currentColor" has no preview in pptx; only HTML renders these faithfully.

[preview-colour] Exported 62 colour(s) to: example-colours.json

Output created: preview-colour-pptx.pptx


